    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just the silence. it's the pointlessness of it all. i look around and i see everything i used to do for him—the walks, the feeding, the constant care—and now it's all just... gone. it feels like i'm just going through the motions for no reason. i'm just so tired of carrying this weight around every single day. it feels like it's never going to stop.",
